s#radixtointexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h1>\r\n<h1 class=>radix toInt Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/sanitization/toInt#radixtointexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Let's create a user model and define a property of 'radix' in the model.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-radix-model\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Through Angular FormBuilder service we create FormGroup in the component.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-radix-component\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Next, we need to write html code.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-radix-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-toInt-radix\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'completetointexample'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h1 class=>Complete toInt Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/sanitization/toInt/decorators#completetointexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h1>\r\n<h1 class=>Complete toInt Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/sanitization/toInt#completetointexample'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Let's create a user model and define a property of 'amount' in the model.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-complete-model\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Through Angular FormBuilder service we create FormGroup in the component.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-complete-component\"></div> \r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Next, we need to write html code.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"toInt-complete-html\"></div> \r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-toInt-complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}